{"tid":2393469,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"GME、AMC、BB、白銀股通通散水 沽空機構Mudrick Capital大賺2億美金","createTime":"2021-02-03T12:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T13:04:17.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc925db427687c236c68bf9255a4e5f725f36c6","tid":2393469,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:45:09.000Z","msg":"上週美國散戶與華爾街沽空機構因為GameStop（美股代號：GME）而引發連場大戰，相信大家已經很清楚事情始末，不在此重複。但多隻被點名的「挾淡倉」股票及商品本週開始出現散水潮。與此同時，雖然多間沽空機構1月蝕錢收場，但Mudrick Capital就在戰役中贏得2億美元，成為大贏家。<br />\n<br />\n大戰主角GameStop股價週一跌30.77％，週二再跌60％報90美元，以週二收市價計，較上週高位483元累跌81.4％。其他wallstreetbets概念股亦無運行，AMC院線（美股代號：AMC）週二跌41.2%；高斯電子（美股代號：KOSS）週二跌42.86%；黑莓（美股代號：BB）週二跌21.05%。<br />\n<br />\n而早前有報道指網民轉戰白銀市場，First Majestic（美股代號：AG）週一升22.08%報22.12美元，週二倒跌24.23%報16.76美元；iShares Silver Trust（美股代號：SLV）週一升7.08%，週二倒跌8.3%；港股中國白銀（815）週一升62.65%，週二跌23.7%，週三再跌9.71%。<br />\n<br />\n正當市場認為「挾淡倉」行動由散戶主導的時候，渾水創辦人Carson Block接受《彭博》訪問時就指，GameStop事件與渾水數星期前被夾淡倉的情況相近，傾向相信這是對沖基金之間的廝殺造成的現象。<br />\n<br />\n而根據《路透》報道，著名沽空機構Melvin Capital於1月份結算資產損失53%；Maplelane Capital蝕45%；D1 Capital虧損20%；Greenlight Capital蝕11%；Point72 Asset Management損失近9%；Citadel虧損3%；Balyasny Asset Management蝕0.5%。<br />\n<br />\n然而，報道引述知情人士指，Jason Mudrick旗下Mudrick Capital在最近幾周的Reddit狂熱中獲利近2億美元，資產規模增加9.8%，是有史以來最好單月表現。Mudrick Capital資產規模約31億美元，今次獲利主要來自同樣被散戶挾淡倉的AMC Entertainment Holdings Inc.的債務和期權，以及通過賣出GameStop的價外認購期權而獲利。"},{"pid":"0e77f43edefea9dcb3765435a46f49dfad3fc30d","tid":2393469,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"一切都係大義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4369151623cce4604d3072695305fcf41fe4c7e2","tid":2393469,"uid":311611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"炒AMC係 on9 仔, <br />\n<br />\n不嬲挾空唔睇股價睇街貨, 成班送錢比人洗.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd85676ed9b7431416e2ef973bfca789480aedf","tid":2393469,"uid":227441,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCSdNs9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCSdNs9.jpg&h=97ca8e45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2a5a55aa0baec1d69358c30fb081faa09b7c78a","tid":2393469,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:57:22.000Z","msg":"大家唔好信，呢D係deep state放出黎既fake news"},{"pid":"cbe96b1577c0929c063f3062225cee4c2ce8129f","tid":2393469,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd85676ed9b7431416e2ef973bfca789480aedf","tid":2393469,"uid":227441,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCSdNs9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCSdNs9.jpg&h=97ca8e45&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b83c5c3d83cc7ef33878397f96c236337050e36","tid":2393469,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd85676ed9b7431416e2ef973bfca789480aedf","tid":2393469,"uid":227441,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCSdNs9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCSdNs9.jpg&h=97ca8e45&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hk